{"tid":1778150,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[飛機post]同狗同村食盆菜，佢話真係驗到二噁英","createTime":"2019-12-10T17:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T13:10:42.000Z","uid":189404,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eea1b8ff705ba22d3d49486606b7930401e73cb4","tid":1778150,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:15:21.000Z","msg":"繼上次話佢老婆聽到我話催淚彈有二噁英生瘡傷精生畸胎喊撚左出黎，真係捉佢老公去驗，結果奶撚哂野。<br />\n<br />\n原來唔知係咪落左order，香港依家無得直接驗，要挖撚左粒瘡d野再抽好多野send去外國驗。結果真係瘡痤瘡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：呢壇野一定同佢計到盡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：點計？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:工傷羅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：政府唔撚公開成份，你吹撚漲佢呀，你拎粒催淚彈去驗拉鳩埋你都似。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:屌我呢世生唔到仔呀，無丁呀！成千萬呀屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：洗唔洗我可以幫下手<br />\n<br />\n之後唔知點解佢納棍出黎想打鳩我，好彩比人㩒住無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03168ef20c26ee2c62118aa3ba7900edc4a14889","tid":1778150,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8995a7f261185242c1038eee41348c35328995bb","tid":1778150,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{